  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Logistic Admin",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Receive and verify shipping and billing documents</li><li>Verify customer shipping requirements and shipment modes</li><li>Process sales orders and billing accurately in ERP system</li><li>Update records in Excel and coordinate with operations team</li><li>Match packing documents with shipment management system (SMS)</li><li>Perform ERP transactions (purchase requests, receipts, stock transfers)</li><li>Conduct weekly and monthly cycle count validation</li><li>Communicate with customers via email, Teams, and phone</li><li>Liaise with internal teams to fulfill customer orders</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Diploma in any field</li><li>Proficient in MS Office</li><li>Minimum 1 year of warehousing or logistics experience</li><li>Detail-oriented and able to work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Willing to work overtime, including weekends and public holidays</li></ul><p><u><strong>Other Information:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Location: East/ Tuas</li><li>Timing: 8.30am - 5.30pm</li><li>Monday to Friday</li></ul><p>Interested candidates please kindly send CV to 89524450</p><p>Lee Mei Kiew Geraldine<br />CEI Reg: R1331173<br />Link2 Manpower Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 22C1131</p><p></p>",
